model.name: Silhouette Mule
model.disambiguatingDescription: This reinterpretation of the Silhouette mule is crafted from glossy glazed calf leather and decorated with engraved, silver-tone studs inspired by historic Louis Vuitton trunks. This model's Monogram Flower-shaped heel, which is a signature of the Silhouette line, is covered in patent Monogram canvas.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• White
  • Glazed calf leather and patent Monogram canvas
  • Leather outsole
  • 8 cm / 3.1-inch heel
  • Monogram Flower-shaped heel
  • Louis Vuitton-engraved studs
  • Made in Italy
